{"tid":1972369,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★廁紙當口罩原料---湖北查獲4600萬片黑心口罩","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T13:22:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06cefa4b086b843098dffacf2621913f7fb56abc","tid":1972369,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2615000/2616803/20200414WEB_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2615000%2F2616803%2F20200414WEB_1024.png&h=3181b79c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新冠肺炎疫情在歐美蔓延，各國民眾紛戴口罩自保，卻傳出有內地口罩廠商為趕工出售圖利、使用品質不符合標準的原料製作口罩。湖北省仙桃市日前查出4600萬片不合格口罩，有廠商拿廁紙製作口罩。<br />\n<br />\n據《封面新聞》報道，湖北仙桃市自疫情爆發後，執法部門共取締273家非法口罩工廠、查獲扣押4600萬片不合格的口罩，市值涉近1億元（人民幣，下同）。報道指出，因為疫情當前，製作口罩的原料熔噴布嚴重缺貨，許多不良業者買不到原料，就拿衞生紙等物品假冒來製作黑心口罩。<br />\n<br />\n曝光的影片中可見，警方剪開黑心口罩發現，比起真正的外科口罩，濾芯極其薄，甚至近乎透明；滲水情況也非常嚴重，合格的口罩幾乎不滲水；醫療用口罩濾芯用熔噴布遇火不燃，黑心口罩卻立即燒起來來，「實際上是用衞生紙代替」。當局目前已將這些不合格的口罩扣押，並擴大規模展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2616803/?fbclid=IwAR2LGf-WjcFO1sy7eMvXBnzYFcBxe3AQ0gI7xlZo05ByE2wkM1hD8eNIi24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2616803%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LGf-WjcFO1sy7eMvXBnzYFcBxe3AQ0gI7xlZo05ByE2wkM1hD8eNIi24&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=e0f73d5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2616803/?fbclid=IwAR2LGf-WjcFO1sy7eMvXBnzYFcBxe3AQ0gI7xlZo05ByE2wkM1hD8eNIi24</a>"},{"pid":"1a7ec3c9d6ead7559d5fa5a2fcb26fdbb936f98e","tid":1972369,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"